sequenceDiagram
    participant K as Klipper
    participant APO as Auto Power Off
    participant M as Moonraker
    participant P as Power Device

    Note over K,APO: Module startup
    K->>APO: _handle_ready()
    APO->>K: reactor.register_timer(_verify_device_state, +10s)
    
    loop Every 10 seconds
        K-->>APO: _verify_device_state(eventtime)
        
        alt Shutdown in progress
            APO->>APO: Check if timeout exceeded
            alt Timeout exceeded (>30s)
                APO->>APO: _reset_shutdown_state()
                APO->>APO: Log "Forced reset after timeout"
            end
        end
        
        APO->>APO: _verify_power_device()
        
        alt Device available and shutdown in progress
            APO->>APO: Detect manual power-on
            APO->>APO: _reset_shutdown_state()
            APO->>APO: Log "Device manually turned on"
        end
        
        APO->>K: Return eventtime + 10.0
    end
    
    Note over K,P: This periodic check allows:
    Note over K,P: 1. Detection of manual power-ons
    Note over K,P: 2. Recovery from stuck shutdown states
    Note over K,P: 3. Maintaining internal state consistency
